    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Variety of fossil resin found in deposits in Burma; usually red in color but may also be pale yellow, golden, or brown. It was used by the Chinese in the manufacture of art objects.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
